################################
## Configuring PicLeaks       ##
################################

1. go to configuration folder
2. open application-sample.ini
3. save it with different file name to temporary location
4. edit the details where marked
5. save the file as application.ini into folder /site/application/configs/
6. launch your browser and visit project's index file (eg. http://localhost/PicLeaks
7. if you see Welcome -screen, installation was successful!)


